  m_text: 'GridFlowSteeringClip Field=Threat Bias=Descend MaxSpeed=2. A static RED hazard continuously stamps a +10 Threat disc nearby; the BLUE agent reads the field GRADIENT and steers DOWN it (descend = flee the threat). Writes LocalTransform.Position DIRECTLY (ignores physics). VISIBLE MOTION: the agent slides away from the hazard each loop.'
